## File Structure & Purpose

### Critical Files (DO modify for content updates)

**`_pages/about.md`** - THE ENTIRE SITE
- Single source of truth for all content
- Pure markdown with consistent formatting
- Sections: About, Employment, Projects, Community, Education, Skills
- Uses anchor links: `## <a name="employment"></a>Employment History`

**`_data/navigation.yml`** - Top Navigation Bar
- Anchor links to sections on homepage
- Format: `url: /#section-name`
- Don't add pages, just section links

**`_config.yml`** - Site Configuration
- Author info (name, bio, avatar, location, employer)
- Site title and description
- Keep profile info updated

**`images/headshot.jpeg`** - Profile Photo
- Current photo is formatted for circular display
- 175x175px circular crop via CSS

### Styling Files (modify carefully)

**`_sass/_variables.scss`** - Colors & Typography
```scss
$primary-color: #2563EB;      // Blue for dates, links, accents
$secondary-color: #7C3AED;     // Purple accent (rarely used)
$darker-gray: #1F2937;         // Main text color
$doc-font-size: 17;            // Base font size
```

**`_sass/_modern-portfolio.scss`** - Custom Styles (94 lines - keep it simple!)
- Section header styling (bold, blue underline)
- Date styling (bold, blue color)
- HR divider styling (gradient lines)
- Spacing and typography
- Smooth scroll behavior

**`assets/css/main.scss`** - Main Stylesheet
- Imports all SCSS files
- Includes `@import "modern-portfolio";`
- Don't modify unless adding new SCSS files

### Files to NEVER Modify

**`_sass/_sidebar.scss`** - Avatar styling is perfect, don't touch!
